answers.body_markdown:
Sounds like you&#39;ll want to make it a higher order function. You pass in some value that you want to check, and you&#39;ll get returned a taker function that will check that. For example:

```
export const makeTaker = arg =&gt; action =&gt; action.type === &#39;ACTION_TYPE&#39; &amp;&amp; action.payload.arg === arg;

// ...

yield take(makeTaker(&#39;hello&#39;))
```
